snippet.title: Mario + Rabbids Kingdom Battle - Demonstration - Nintendo E3 2017
snippet.description:
Check out the gameplay for Mario + Rabbids Kingdom Battle at the Nintendo Show floor at E3 2017. 

The Mushroom Kingdom has been torn apart by a mysterious vortex, transporting the Rabbids into the once-peaceful area, splintering this beloved land. To bring order back to the Kingdom, Mario, Luigi, Princess Peach, and Yoshi team up with Rabbids heroes in a journey through four different worlds. Mario + Rabbids® Kingdom Battle will be available exclusively for Nintendo Switch on August 29, 2017.
